---
/**
 * Hero. Single column, left aligned.
 *
 * The page opens on a plain statement of what the crate is and what it does,
 * following the Katzoff introduction formula (docs/writing_guides/
 * ClarityTechnicalReporting.pdf, p. 9): background, contribution, scope. No
 * figure: the capabilities section below carries the code and the run output,
 * which is where a reader can check the claims.
 */
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">DeepCausality · CFD</p>
    <h1>Counterfactual fluid dynamics</h1>

    <p class="tagline">
      A Rust crate that marches a compressible flow with plasma chemistry,
      navigation and control in one typed process, then forks the marched state
      to evaluate alternative commands.
    </p>

    <p class="sub">
      Three solver families share one interface and one scalar type: a
      DEC-native incompressible solver, quantized tensor-train compressible
      marchers, and fitted analytic closures. A program selects per problem and
      composes them into one coupled run.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/tutorial/">
        Start the tutorial
        <span class="btn-ico" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/validation/">
        Validation status
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero { padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-4) var(--space-7); }
  @media (min-width: 720px) { .hero { padding: var(--space-9) var(--space-5) var(--space-8); } }

  .hero-inner { max-width: var(--w-panel); margin: 0 auto; }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw + 0.5rem, 3.5rem);
    line-height: var(--lh-display);
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-display);
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-5);
    max-width: 18ch;
  }
  .tagline {
    font-size: var(--t-h3);
    line-height: var(--lh-h3);
    color: var(--fg-1);
    max-width: var(--measure-lede);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
  }
  .sub {
    color: var(--fg-1);
    font-size: var(--t-body-sm);
    max-width: var(--measure);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
  }

  .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-3); margin-bottom: 0; }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 var(--space-5);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    font-size: var(--t-body-sm);
    font-weight: var(--fw-heading);
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: transform var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),
                background-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),
                border-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),
                color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--accent-ink); }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 90%, white);
    border-color: transparent;
    border-bottom-color: transparent;
  }
  .btn-ico { transition: transform var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out); }
  .btn-primary:hover .btn-ico { transform: translateX(2px); }
  .btn-ghost { color: var(--fg-0); border-color: var(--line-2); }
  .btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--fg-2);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 5%, transparent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--fg-2);
  }
</style>
